{"tid":582375,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[奧斯卡] 陶傑鬧賽果：「左膠」分豬肉　《忘形水》不值攞獎","createTime":"2018-03-06T06:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T07:42:13.000Z","uid":46356,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62a077e803f8037b8f73cc3f8a772ac77ffa27fd","tid":582375,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180306/20323207?_ga=2.35927845.441509775.1520298991-1400460374.1520298991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F20323207%3F_ga%3D2.35927845.441509775.1520298991-1400460374.1520298991&d=YJGkDyvkR4pa3We%2BlnO0kpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=087a3a3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F20323207%3F_ga%3D2.35927845.441509775.1520298991-1400460374.1520298991&h=4f7c4929\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180306/20323207?_ga=2.35927845.441509775.1520298991-1400460374.1520298991</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>陶傑鬧賽果：「左膠」分豬肉</strong><br />\n<br />\n第90屆奧斯卡頒獎禮塵埃落定，《忘形水》奪四獎成大贏家，但名嘴陶傑認為《忘》片不值攞獎，他昨日接受電話訪問時，以「左膠」分豬肉形容賽果：「《忘形水》我睇到一半，唔係好頂得順就起身。呢套戲應該係《鐘樓駝俠》（The Hunchback of Notre Dame）、《美女與野獸》（Beauty and the Beast）講過晒，今次將野生動物加一個21世紀、環保綠色阿凡達色彩，加埋導演被人話抄襲，我覺得冇乜新意。可能我唔夠公道，冇睇到尾，可能到尾開估出嚟好正。我睇意識形態，女主角演一個啞女，好明顯係想政治正確，擺明為攞獎。所以我覺得呢部戲係不值最佳電影。」<br />\n<br />\n至於心目中最佳電影為《黑暗對峙》或者《廣告牌殺人事件》：「呢兩套有新意會係《廣告牌》，好過舊年套好惡頂嘅《月亮喜歡藍》（Moonlight），呢啲同性戀電影《斷背山》（Brokeback Mountain）畀咗已經夠，舊年畀埋黑人，如果為咗政治正確而畀獎呢，就應該畀《戰雲密報》嘅梅姨。」雖然《廣告牌》亦有女性主義、政治正確，但故事講得有新意，有技巧就是好戲：「套戲都左左哋，雖然佢表達手法都幾右，好似滿口粗口男人婆、用侏儒配女主角，都唔緊要，呢啲先係最佳電影，喺矛盾度搵到統一。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：何永寧<br />\n<br />\n■梅姨主演的《戰雲密報》，在政治正確底下都應該有獎。劇照<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180306/large/06ec1p106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180306%2Flarge%2F06ec1p106.jpg&h=a7d7b539&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06c7a7887f81beeeaaafbdf47950ac2388a5b532","tid":582375,"uid":13885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3c145625cba1c2b8c64871a78a66c3a59359d8","tid":582375,"uid":173397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f719fff2aac09128d5b8986eda61baf3bda28179","tid":582375,"uid":28001,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"恕我膚淺唔夠藝術家性格<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得The shape of water 真係好好睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申返: Guillermo del Toro fans"},{"pid":"5f2489149d7d056ad9622f4002797e6b9fbff77e","tid":582375,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc3c145625cba1c2b8c64871a78a66c3a59359d8","tid":582375,"uid":173397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"唔係呀<br />\n我話唔值，可以拍得浪漫啲，冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得幾個正評"},{"pid":"714bd400f1473c08d9e5197d2439fe731ee9868d","tid":582375,"uid":22889,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f719fff2aac09128d5b8986eda61baf3bda28179","tid":582375,"uid":28001,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"恕我膚淺唔夠藝術家性格<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得The shape of water 真係好好睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申返: Guillermo del Toro fans"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T07:25:21.000Z","msg":"就係藝術家性格先鍾意SOW<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常啲人屌都係屌技術層面（e.g.